{"tid":2106203,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖無字/你問我答] 埃塞俄比亞12日之旅","createTime":"2020-07-13T07:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T09:13:42.000Z","uid":38955,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8970af5632c2274559b860c48ac687c2033ea4a0","tid":2106203,"uid":38955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T07:45:07.000Z","msg":"上年9/10月去 純粹趁仲記得打番出黎紀錄下<br />\n大概打番d highlights出黎 唔會逐日打哂<br />\nTotal去左12日<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V9UBNwG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV9UBNwG.png&h=6a1304e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上面個堆係呢十幾日主要去既城市<br />\n以首都addis ababa為界分左開南北2邊 <br />\n北邊主要睇自然景觀(Danakil depression) <br />\n有活火山 琉璜湖 仲有埃塞俄比亞版天空之鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n南邊睇原住民部落 國家公園同d歷史人文野為主<br />\n全程12日都係跟local tour 有司機同某d地方有armed guard帶住 <br />\n (有台灣人試過全程自己玩唔跟任何guide 仲出埋書 有興趣可以買黎睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我自己自問做唔到咁hardcore)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/keWMqmP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkeWMqmP.png&h=4ca4fdb7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kqd3sz9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkqd3sz9.png&h=f409e8ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XrqELmR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXrqELmR.jpg&h=bd1da5ec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K5qM9Oz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK5qM9Oz.jpg&h=4b0757f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yRGpb10.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyRGpb10.png&h=d6802dd4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qZ6D0Vq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqZ6D0Vq.png&h=f8526de1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EeJ69OQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"ht