<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gatyQbB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgatyQbB.jpg&h=8213c5d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BEfpWRC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBEfpWRC.png&h=b16507f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/htVmeDi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhtVmeDi.png&h=def839b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4a950997d6f0a8a68683af1d1da28a1ba8ad90e","tid":2106203,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T07:48:00.000Z","msg":"係咪就係好撚毒個d水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2009a8650b2a1f0c2798d4a7e45351d7cc936457","tid":2106203,"uid":38955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T07:51:03.000Z","msg":"落機之後係首都addis ababa留左半日<br />\n之後轉坐內陸機去北部danakil depression<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KFR1ewc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKFR1ewc.png&h=ff06a893&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為北部既tour淨係政府拍定既旅行社先可以帶<br />\n所以同行會有其他外國人一齊 大約廿個人到<br />\n另外北面可以話完全無住同食既地方 <br />\n所以同行又會有廚師跟埋黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全程3日2夜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6rOu7RT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6rOu7RT.png&h=6bfaa1b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kZPFu5h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkZPFu5h.png&h=ad5da0ba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5U2DgLm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5U2DgLm.png&h=cd038afb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後3日2夜差唔多餐餐都係食類似既野<br />\n不得不提係幾好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大部份以薯仔為主<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BfcvSiL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBfcvSiL.png&h=b3687147&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全程坐越野車入 dun左7個鐘左右由市區到火山區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HgrTP6B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHgrTP6B.png&h=a6d2c24a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢地煮野食既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全露天 好彩夜晚唔算熱<br />\n入夜之後開始上山睇活火山 來回2個鐘左右<br />\n路唔算難行 但因為摸黑行一定要有頭燈/手機光源<br />\n有好幾次都差d仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上到去可惜既係有d熔岩係前年地震已經流走左<br />\n現時睇到既已經無之前既咁壯觀<br />\n(有興趣睇可以自己google Erta Ale)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://vimeo.com/437766893\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2F437766893&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxBzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=d3ebc529\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://vimeo.com/437766893</a><br />\n呢條片係接近山頂拍 好彩都仲可以睇到小部份爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n現場係好撚熱 同埋行埋去一定要帶Gas mask防琉璜味<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9ZDyP6G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9ZDyP6G.png&h=6f1b4278&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qq1TP6L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqq1TP6L.png&h=e5c7778b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我地訓既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最深刻係夜晚有次醒左 一開眼成個天空都係星<br />\n之前已經係西藏睇過次星夜 但埃國呢次係更加光同清 文字形容唔到有幾難忘"},{"pid":"ee4040dc24928df1b6d874561da4a534b10754b0","tid":2106203,"uid":269681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:25:36.000Z","msg":"洗左幾錢 食完d野會唔會肚痛"},{"pid":"9b835cb47f5416bdb1669afad9137e3391500d1c","tid":2106203,"uid":38955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4a950997d6f0a8a68683af1d1da28a1ba8ad90e","tid":2106203,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T07:48:00.00